enkloster des Spätmittelalters.  aDespite the remarkable texts that it contains, the “Hermetschwil Prayer Book” has been largely neglected by scholars until now. This volume comprehensively presents the early 15th century German-language prayer book from a Benedictine cloister in Aargau.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aChurch historyyMiddle Ages, 600-1500. 0aDevotional literaturexHistory and criticism. 0aDevotional literaturey15th century. 0aPrayer bookszSwitzerlandxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aPrayer bookszSwitzerlandy15th century. 4aEidgenossenschaft (Schweiz). 4aFrauenkloster. 4aFrömmigkeit. 4aGebetbuch. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aPrayer book.  aSwiss confederation.  aconvent.  apiety.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2013z9783110317251oZDB-23-DLW0 cprintz978311031630840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311031644540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110316445423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110316445/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2013  aZDB-23-DLWb2013  aZDB-23-GLCc2000d2014